Class AbstractFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>

  • gw.plugin.contact.findduplicates.querybuilder.AbstractFieldExpression<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FieldExpression<T>, _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractCompositeFieldExpression, EqualFieldExpression, InFieldExpression, StartsWithFieldExpression

    public class AbstractFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
implements FieldExpression<T>, _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject
    A base implementation for the {@link FieldExpression} methods. The operate method will check isValid before calling abstractdoOperate which has to be overriden by subclasses.
